<br>
Yes - your points are well taken.<br>
Yes - it is frustrating at times.<br>
Yes - I believe our class needs help also.<br>
<br>
However...  I will say that overall, the game can be fun and enjoyable. <br>
<br>
Our server is home to quite a few large guilds. Guilds that have such high caliber that pumps more mudflation that most other servers will never see.<br>
<br>
On Veeshan, our main selling area is North Freeport. Stop by and visit us as a guest sometime - you will be amazed at what you see for sale. As an example - while strolling through NFP today - I had the opportunity to purchase a Zlandicar's Heart should I care to. Now I didn't catch the going cost, but I do know and have read that that is a very nice item. Most folks would keep it, rather than sell. I have never seen anything like that on the other 2 servers I have chars on: Luclin and Tunare. Veeshan is a twink server.<br>
<br>
